title: Leader Rodgers: “Stop the Abortion on Demand Until Birth Act and Uphold the Value, the Dignity, and the Potential of Every Person’s Life.”
description: Washington, D.C. — Energy and Commerce Committee Republican Leader Cathy McMorris Rodgers (R-WA) spoke today before the House Committee on Rules in opposition to H.R. 3755, the Abortion on Demand Until Birth Act.

title: Putting Kids First: Addressing COVID-19’s Impacts on Children
